NAME

AssetCacheManagerService — Service to manage macOS Content Caching

SYNOPSIS

AssetCacheManagerService

DESCRIPTION

AssetCacheManagerService manages the computer's Content Cache.

There are no configuration options to AssetCacheManagerService. Users should not run AssetCacheManagerService manually.

DIAGNOSTICS

AssetCacheManagerService logs to the os_log(3) subsystem com.apple.AssetCacheServices category Manager.
